window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Lex </b></p> <p>They've taken my girl. My little bird.</p> <p>I'll do whatever it takes to get her back, even if it means I have to level this city to the ground. They've woken the monster, and I'll be damn sure my face is the last one they see before I send them all to hell. </p> <p><b>Wren </b></p> <p><i>Beaten. Bruised. Broken. </i></p> <p>They want me weak and submissive, but they've underestimated me. I'm no damsel. They've taken me from Lex, and I know he'll do everything to get me back. After all, I'm the queen of this city, and my rightful place is next to the king. </p> <p>It's time to end this war.</p> <p><b><i>Twisted King</i></b><b> is the second and final book in the Twisted City Duet. It cannot be listened to as a stand-alone.</b></p> <p><b>A dark, dangerous, and deliciously sinful mafia romance.</b></p>"; 
